          <div class="tech-overview">
            <h3>Hybrid Encryption System</h3>
            <p>
              Quasar uses a sophisticated hybrid encryption approach combining RSA-OAEP and AES-GCM
              to deliver both security and performance. Each message is protected with unique
              encryption keys.
            </p>
          </div>

